GET
Daftar Rekomendasi
foryou
Uji Endpoint
Mengambil daftar drama rekomendasi utama.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/foryou/1?lang=in"
GET
Rilis Terbaru
newlist
Uji Endpoint
Daftar drama yang baru saja dirilis.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/new/1?lang=in&pageSize=10"
GET
Peringkat Populer
rank
Uji Endpoint
Daftar drama paling populer saat ini.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/rank/1?lang=in"
GET
Filter & Klasifikasi
classify
Uji Endpoint
Filter drama berdasarkan Genre/Kategori.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/classify?lang=in&pageNo=1&genre=1357&sort=1"
GET
Pencarian
search
Uji Endpoint
Mencari drama berdasarkan kata kunci.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/search/ceo/1?lang=in"
GET
Saran Pencarian
suggest
Uji Endpoint
Auto-complete saran kata kunci.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/suggest/cinta?lang=in"
GET
Daftar Episode
chapters
Uji Endpoint
Mengambil daftar seluruh episode.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/chapters/42000000722?lang=in"
GET
Detail Episode
chaptersDetail
Uji Endpoint
Mengambil detail lengkap seluruh episode.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/chapters/detail/42000000722?lang=in"
GET
Stream Video (GET)
watch
Uji Endpoint
Link streaming video episode tertentu.


Salin
curl -X GET "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/watch/42000000722/0?lang=in&source=search_result"
POST
Stream Player (POST)
player
Uji Endpoint
Alternatif streaming dengan JSON body.


Salin
curl -X POST "https://sapi.dramabox.be/api/watch/player?lang=in"
-H "Content-Type: application/json"
-d '{
    "bookId": "42000000722",
    "chapterIndex": 10,
    "lang": "in"
}'